    """
Get Projections
"""

body = project(med_np * body_mask, crop_size=256)
lung = project(med_np * lung_mask, crop_size=256)
bones = project(med_np * bones_mask, crop_size=256)
chest = project(med_np * body_mask * (~lung_mask), crop_size=256)
plot([body, lung, bones, chest], ("Body", "Lung", "Bones", "Outer"))
    """ Get Projections """ body = project(med_np * body_mask, crop_size=256) lung = project(med_np * lung_mask, crop_size=256) bones = project(med_np * bones_mask, crop_size=256) chest = project(med_np * body_mask * (~lung_mask), crop_size=256) plot([body, lung, bones, chest], ("Body", "Lung", "Bones", "Outer"))
